CAM PC: 
Replace the string in /etc/hostname with "cam"
Add to /etc/hosts:
192.168.100.95    cam
192.168.100.96    car


CAR PC: 
Replace the string in /etc/hostname with "car"
192.168.100.95    cam
192.168.100.96    car


IPs an Netzwerkkarten
Manta
PC: Intel Netzwerkkarte Heckansicht oben links (169.254.200.184/16 @ A0:36:9F:68:57:4F)
Manta: 169.254.200.185/16 @ 00-0F-31-4C-90-19




